<hr />
<p>I first drafted this in January 2015. Now it's finally done. I cannot at this point remember who to credit with feedback, because so many people gave it.</p>
<p><span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/troyl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(451071); return false;">TroyL</a></span> outright created a great many of the entries on this list during a single massive brainstorming session where he unloaded ideas on me over a phone call and I wrote as fast as I could to keep up.</p>
<p><span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/theduckman" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(224440); return false;">TheDuckman</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sophia-light" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(306685); return false;">Sophia Light</a></span>, and <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dreverettmann" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(323946); return false;">DrEverettMann</a></span> also had huge influences on this list, via a long history of work on O5 characters.</p>
<p><span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;">Decibelles</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1229263); return false;">Roget</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(637830); return false;">SoullessSingularity</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dexanote" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(481882); return false;">Dexanote</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kestin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1827815); return false;">Kestin</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735681); return false;">TwistedGears</a></span>, <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/theduckman" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(224440); return false;">TheDuckman</a></span>, and <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/troyl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(451071); return false;">TroyL</a></span> (and many others I have certainly forgotten) gave a lot of very helpful feedback on this list. If I forgot to mention you, and you gave me feedback on this, remind me to add you. &lt;3</p>
<p>Finally: All feedback welcome. Nothing here is set in stone. :)</p>

